{"tid":378551,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"無法理解IU的時尚世界！IU造型師 有苦自己知","createTime":"2017-08-28T14:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T17:45:24.000Z","uid":34643,"like":28,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1681f5417248da5894ddab8efbcd10ff6c93e17a","tid":378551,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:44:52.000Z","msg":"昨日播出的《孝利家民宿》中，李孝利、IU和客人丹利一起去逛了濟州島當地懷舊風格的店，女人們一起逛衣服真的就是不一樣啊（笑）！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_38248115b27fcafa6fec0fc2857e1993/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-08-28/97581-535805.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_38248115b27fcafa6fec0fc2857e1993%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-08-28%2F97581-535805.jpg&h=6f0491cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIU挑選了自己喜歡的衣服還有紫色包包在照鏡子時，結果李孝利看到竟然問她：「知恩啊！那個包包真的好看嗎？」IU也回了：「恩？不好看嗎？」後來李孝利只好說：「我們的喜好不同，確實不同啊！」還一直檢查IU挑選的衣服，問她這真的好看嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_852282136330d3d3a4a268d421b997ba/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-08-28/97581-535797.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_852282136330d3d3a4a268d421b997ba%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-08-28%2F97581-535797.png&h=296c1aa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_bf6daa3e4595a96d6dec21cf9d0d8fec/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-08-28/97581-535798.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_bf6daa3e4595a96d6dec21cf9d0d8fec%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-08-28%2F97581-535798.png&h=5dc4d5e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來李孝利也提到：「這次的歌曲（《Palette》）中，有喜歡土氣的這種歌詞吧！原來這是你的真實寫照啊！」看到IU邊挑選邊說好看可愛的表情，而李孝利站在一旁則是一直覺得驚訝（笑），兩人喜歡的東西果然不同，還一直叫丹利阻止IU！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_cbe974420e6bbf9a4cac8d94c4afb181/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-08-28/97581-535800.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_cbe974420e6bbf9a4cac8d94c4afb181%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-08-28%2F97581-535800.png&h=9a8aeb8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_653b4780760143a3a2377a17189356c9/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-08-28/97581-535801.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_653b4780760143a3a2377a17189356c9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-08-28%2F97581-535801.png&h=2ca92d2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到另外一家店購物的時候也一樣有趣，一直無法放棄紅色和橘色衣服的IU（笑）！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_3ca5ccf52a20f7eeed032fb2377c3a0f/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-08-28/97581-535820.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_3ca5ccf52a20f7eeed032fb2377c3a0f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-08-28%2F97581-535820.png&h=2307d1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_7475ae1ccdb9a4611d1648c2cb33ea23/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-08-28/97581-535821.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_7475ae1ccdb9a4611d1648c2cb33ea23%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-08-28%2F97581-535821.png&h=8eb8bf12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n節目播出後，IU的造型師也在IG上面發文寫道：「每次看到知恩買回來的衣服，真的經常會說『為什麼買這個回來呢？』，但很神奇的是知恩又能很好的消化，但是也...」，IU發文看到也回覆：「也是害怕造型師覺得丟臉，每次去機場的時候自己也會苦惱一番，然後也是有好好穿的。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_0aa899d9825156b50698cc9c291aace5/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-08-28/97581-535802.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_0aa899d9825156b50698cc9c291aace5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-08-28%2F97581-535802.jpg&h=36aee0f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdc52845a2c35c0a218db075b25962ac0ab73ba5","tid":378551,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:46:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FqhSQyo1u4Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/